    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167210/extras/07454b143553f716c487b834532646a0.poster.avif?t=1746992140\" width=544 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167210/extras/07454b143553f716c487b834532646a0.webm?t=1746992140\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167210/extras/07454b143553f716c487b834532646a0.mp4?t=1746992140\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >欢迎来到深渊的世界! </h2>一个最黑暗的恐惧和痛苦的记忆在你眼前浮现的地方。准备好被拉入一场独特而惊险的冒险，在那里你将不得不与其他勇敢的冒险家合作，面对你最糟糕的噩梦，克服你最深的创伤。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167210/extras/a76800a2eb7324922e621d5fbd23dae2.avif?t=1746992140\" width=616 height=87 /></span><br><br>在《告别》中，你将沉浸在一个黑暗和神秘的世界中，你的合作技能将在控制3个不同角色的每一步中受到考验。你会找到勇气来面对你最糟糕的恐惧和记忆吗？只有你能发现这一点!<br><br>你准备好加入这个令人兴奋和具有挑战性的冒险了吗？那就准备好探索一个充满危险的世界，揭开你自己恐惧和欲望的最黑暗的秘密。永别在等着你!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167210/extras/f7ec43f2176a6a4d1ae9b1681f8dc4a0.avif?t=1746992140\" width=616 height=87 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167210/extras/3feee6273d06043f3db41107c114b6e6.poster.avif?t=1746992140\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167210/extras/3feee6273d06043f3db41107c114b6e6.webm?t=1746992140\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167210/extras/3feee6273d06043f3db41107c114b6e6.mp4?t=1746992140\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span